RACE.FOOTNOTES: CARIBBEAN BREEZE five to six paths off the inside down the backstretch just off the duel, tucked three wide into the turn advancing to issue a challenge midway on that bend, knocked heads with BERNT AGAIN from the five-sixteenths and spun three wide for home, dueled through the stretch to the finish in game fashion and just got a nostril on the wire over her main rival. FOLLOW THE FED three wide in pursuit, came under coaxing at the three-eighths, angled four wide into upper stretch and tired. DASHING DELLA coaxed from the start, dueled from the four path down the backstretch with BERNT AGAIN to her inside, tucked to the two path into the turn and came under coaxing three furlongs out when being shaken off by the top one, spun just off the inside into upper stretch in retreat and faltered in the drive. NEVER PERSONAL four to five paths off the inside down the backstretch, tucked to the two path through the turn under urging from the seven-sixteenths, swung four to five wide for home, made no impact, then was reported to have bled. FRANKIE KNOWS BEST chased three then two wide under coaxing from the seven-sixteenths, angled six wide into upper stretch, trailed.
